mineclub-expanded.config.outbidsound.des:
Plays a Minecraft bee death sound if someone outbids you. 
§4This can get a little loud.
mineclub-expanded.config.autogg.descript: Makes you say gg right after the end of the game.
mineclub-expanded.config.outbidvolume.de:
Controls the volume of the outbid sound 
§4The option 'Outbid Notification Sound' needs to be turned on for this to work.
mineclub-expanded.config.richpresence.co:
Enables Rich Presence 
§4You need to set the server address to 'mineclub.com' or 'play.mineclub.com' for this to work 
Additionally, RP doesn't support speed tag at the moment
